_sText:
De_hydrofire by Sk3tch at www.sk3maps.com
-----------------------------------------

NOTE:  This is the prior version to de_hydroco.  Many people feel this is the better map due to FPS issues and layout.  So instead of getting rid of de_hydrofire_b1, I decided to make it a final.

As compared to de_hydroco, the differences are listed below:

-The sky and environment are a more interesting orange hue.
-Added a overhead view as opposed to the betas not having one.
-Alot more simple on the details along with MUCH BETTER frame rates.
-A NAV file included (without place markers) PAKRATed into the map
-No gun racks
-No exploding bridge
-More fast paced fun!
